,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:15:34.000Z","msg":"鬼剃頭又稱圓禿(alopecia areata)，相信是由免疫系統出現問題而成。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UzSLdk7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUzSLdk7.jpg&h=6838e949&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n審視圓禿病人的基因後，的而且確發現有不少病人均持有與免疫細胞在發展方面有關的基因變異。<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有科學家透過研究（Ref2)，證實外表持有Jag1蛋白質的免疫系統細胞，與髮囊幹細胞表面的Notch1蛋白質觸碰後，便會觸發髮囊幹細胞再生，讓頭髮在皮膚上持續生長。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQtRTmd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQtRTmd.jpg&h=1678c7b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）另外亦有人體實驗研究（Ref1)，注射Interlukin2(激發某系列的免疫細胞)到圓禿病人後，六個月後可見明顯效果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DKv8VzB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDKv8VzB.png&h=c9931ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）圖中為老鼠的髮囊切片，可見髮囊附近的確有免疫細胞聚居。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q98Oa7Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ98Oa7Z.png&h=f5cdf162&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n集合多方證據來看，免疫系統與頭髮生長有著莫大的關係，針對免疫系統來治理脫髮或許會成為一道重要出路。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpotatopigtongue%2F&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=156a7497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/potatopigtongue/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamadermatology/fullarticle/10.1001/jamadermatol.2014.504\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjamadermatology%2Ffullarticle%2F10.1001%2Fjamadermatol.2014.504&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=463e7f27\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jamanetwork.com/journals/jamadermatology/fullarticle/10.1001/jamadermatol.2014.504</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.cell.com/action/showPdf?pii=S0092-8674%2817%2930529-9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cell.com%2Faction%2FshowPdf%3Fpii%3DS0092-8674%252817%252930529-9&d=Z5fxCpLMP6GgpQ63MmTuwoRM%2FwdnRWUJBfohchWxIRY%3D&h=22636f3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cell.com/action/showPdf?pii=S0092-8674%2817%2930529-9</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T22:29:02.000Z","msg":"鬼剃頭會自然生番啲頭髮？"},{"pid":"4f7f8eea537beabec38f68b79c4f58f4e3cf9727","tid":2300693,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378441c05b83d635ce7291841e91718eb31da271","tid":2300693,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40eb3fbf989cf1635d56ff5fd3e77087f90c61ad","tid":2300693,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b77561bdb8c8569f9e8434111f78a5db1a549f9","tid":2300693,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:09:24.000Z","msg":"情緒影響會有咁嚴重？我係咪應該開心D定點？<br />\n起初我以為自己運動不足，走去做運動，過左幾個月又發現無幫助，仲有最近大半年晚上無眼訓嘅感覺，攪到大部份日子3-6am先走上床訓"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:58:29.000Z","msg":"最初嗰陣係瞓咗落床都瞓唔着？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n抑鬱係失眠同事睡都有機會<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n見你話你情緒都冇乜特別，咁會唔會覺得以前有興趣做嘅事而家都好無趣？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T21:12:56.000Z","msg":"我一訓上床15分鐘就訓著，<br />\n&quot;咁會唔會覺得以前有興趣做嘅事而家都好無趣？&quot; &lt;&lt;&lt; 依個真係有，<br />\n以前有興趣做嘅事而家都好無趣，同埋好似成日都唔夠時間生活咁"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T02:22:21.000Z","msg":"失去興趣嗰度可唔可以具體啲講吓？"},{"pid":"f6f39d0f35623d9d5d81b76f6e6f213891dba6d0","tid":2300693,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f7f8eea537beabec38f68b79c4f58f4e3cf9727","tid":2300693,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"378441c05b83d635ce7291841e91718eb31da271","tid":2300693,"uid":193642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40eb3fbf989cf1635d56ff5fd3e77087f90c61ad","tid":2300693,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T18:58:29.000Z","msg":"最初嗰陣係瞓咗